OL,5, The bosses of two energy firms are     
OL,6, calling for green levies on bills to be
OL,7, scrapped to help customers facing      
OL,8, higher prices.                         
OL,10,FThe founder of Ecotricity described the
OL,11,Flevies on energy bills as a "stealth   
OL,12,Ftax" of hundreds of pounds a year.     
OL,14,FCentrica's boss is also urging         
OL,15,Fgovernment to fund green programmes    
OL,16,Fthrough general taxation instead.      
OL,18,FThousands of households have seen their
OL,19,Fenergy bills rise in recent months.    
